			<description><![CDATA[<h3 class="story-teaser">By <a href="https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/112-brett-davidson">Brett Davidson</a></h3>
<div class="story-intro">
<p><a href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-last-redoubt/69-pallin-of-asphodelos/229-minotaur-part-1"><img class="story-thumb" src="https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/davidson-dark-palace-thumb.jpg" alt="A pentagonal building in darkness, seen from above." /></a></p>
<p class="story-teaser">The Monstruwacan entered the Watch compound in his own good time, the shadow of his accumulated fame falling before him. "So say, he was one of us, so say none can read his mind, so say he was Out before, so say he slew monsters — and men..."</p>
</div>
